# Trendyol Validation Reference

## Which Validator to Call

| Situation | Tool |
|---|---|
| Full request (params + headers + body) | `validateRequest(endpointKey, marketplace, pathParams, queryParams, headers, body)` |
| Body only | `validatePayload(endpointKey, payload, marketplace)` |
| Product attributes vs category | `validateProductAgainstCategoryAttributes(categoryAttributesResponse, productItems)` |

Always prefer `validateRequest`. Always pass `marketplace` explicitly.

For createProducts or updateUnapprovedProducts — both validators required:
1. `validateRequest`
2. `validateProductAgainstCategoryAttributes`

If user doesn't have getCategoryAttributes response yet: _"Please call getCategoryAttributes({categoryId: YOUR_ID}) first so I can validate attributes."_

## Error Codes

| Code | Fix |
|---|---|
| `MISSING_REQUIRED_FIELD` | Add the missing field |
| `INVALID_VAT_RATE` | TR: 0, 1, 10, or 20. GLOBAL: country-specific |
| `INVALID_PRICE_RELATION` | listPrice must be >= salePrice |
| `DUPLICATE_BARCODES` | Remove duplicate barcodes |
| `DUPLICATE_CONTENT_IDS` | Remove duplicate contentIds |
| `INVALID_AUTHORIZATION_FORMAT` | Use "Basic base64(apiKey:apiSecret)" |
| `INVALID_SUPPLIER_ID_FORMAT` | X-Supplier-Id must be numeric string |
| `NO_MUTABLE_FIELD` | updatePriceAndInventory needs quantity, salePrice, or listPrice |
| `QUANTITY_EXCEEDS_LIMIT` | Max 20000 units per product |
| `EMPTY_ITEMS_ARRAY` | Add at least one item |
| `MISSING_REQUIRED_PATH_PARAM` | Add path parameter |
| `INVALID_DELIVERY_DURATION` | deliveryDuration must be 1 when fastDeliveryType is set |

## Warning Codes

| Code | Action |
|---|---|
| `IMAGE_URL_NOT_HTTPS` | Change to HTTPS |
| `WRONG_ATTRIBUTE_FORMAT_FOR_CREATE` | Use `attributeValueId` (singular) + `customAttributeValue` for createProducts |
| `WRONG_ATTRIBUTE_FORMAT_FOR_UPDATE` | Use `attributeValueIds` (array) + `attributeValue` for update endpoints |
| `ATTRIBUTES_FULL_SEND_REQUIRED` | Send ALL attributes when any attribute is updated in updateApprovedProductContent |
| `MISSING_VARIANTER_ATTRIBUTE` | Add for correct variant grouping |
| `MISSING_SLICER_ATTRIBUTE` | Add for correct catalog card separation |
| `PAGE_SIZE_PRODUCT_EXCEEDS_LIMIT` | page × size must not exceed 10000 |
| `MISSING_CREDENTIAL_HEADER` | Add Authorization and X-Supplier-Id before real execution |

## validateProductAgainstCategoryAttributes Errors

| Code | Fix |
|---|---|
| `MISSING_REQUIRED_ATTRIBUTE` | Add the required attribute with a value |
| `REQUIRED_ATTRIBUTE_VALUE_MISSING` | Provide attributeValueIds or attributeValue |
| `CUSTOM_VALUE_NOT_ALLOWED` | allowCustom=false — use predefined IDs from getCategoryAttributeValues |
| `MULTIPLE_VALUES_NOT_ALLOWED` | allowMultipleAttributeValues=false — send only one ID |
| `UNKNOWN_ATTRIBUTE` | attributeId not in category — verify getCategoryAttributes |

## Presenting Results

- **Errors** (blocking): explain what is wrong, what was received, exactly how to fix
- **Warnings** (non-blocking): explain and let user decide
- Never say payload is "ready" when errors exist
- No errors: "Schema validation passed."